# RClinVarbitration source notices

## DuckDB C extension headers

`tools/ext/duckdb_capi/v1.5.0/` through `v1.5.4/` contain the exact DuckDB
C extension headers for every bundled `C_STRUCT_UNSTABLE` artifact. Each
pinned upstream revision and repaired-header checksum is recorded in that
version's `duckdb_headers.json`; DuckDB is licensed under the MIT License.

## libxml2

The native extension links the host libxml2 library through `pkg-config`; it
does not bundle libxml2. libxml2 is MIT-licensed. The extension uses only the
forward-reader API and relies on its zlib-enabled XML.GZ support.

## ClinVarbitration decision policy

The SQL decision policy is an attributed disease-specific adaptation of
Centre for Population Genomics ClinVarbitration 2.2.11, pinned to upstream
commit `658b9f241eb2d43aa11214b153b19c1e18a16337` at
`https://github.com/populationgenomics/clinvarbitration`.

